{"tid":2223650,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"想去亞美尼亞參戰","createTime":"2020-09-30T04:01:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T05:40:07.000Z","uid":222614,"like":19,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"cf2e5d01cbe6d51f512b39a837ad3dcd953b3f00","tid":2223650,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T04:01:24.000Z","msg":"study 完亞美尼亞段歷史覺得佢地好慘，ww1 畀火雞國屠殺左150 萬人<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Armenian_Genocide#Conflict_in_the_Balkans_and_Russia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FArmenian_Genocide%23Conflict_in_the_Balkans_and_Russia&d=uIqzu4H250jM%2FFVIgxmQWAAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=b0a5888c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Armenian_Genocide#Conflict_in_the_Balkans_and_Russia</a><br />\n<br />\n到左今日火雞國嘅爾多奸又想恰鳩佢地<br />\n<br />\n蛾同亞美尼亞並無真交情，所以普丁得個睇字同得把口叫佢地冷靜<br />\n<br />\n亞美尼亞以基督徒為主，係國際上無乜朋友，武器又過時，同火雞打實輸得好甘<br />\n<br />\n即使係咁，我都願意去同佢地一齊參戰，佢地同我都係基督嘅追隨者，係我嘅弟兄姐妹，天國嘅家人<br />\n<br />\n唔知爾多奸想點對付佢地，再上演大屠殺？<br />\n<br />\n真心想同佢地一齊抵抗突厥狗，就算死都願意"},{"pid":"f33536bab2eb69ddc5dbd566aed2d185b29fb3ce","tid":2223650,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T04:03:22.000Z","msg":"my Armenian brothers and sisters <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49ca8561189d59b3650615ae7b9b97efd2ff75cf","tid":2223650,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T04:04:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc099b7e24ecd7c13a588b13bb85efdf67f5219e","tid":2223650,"uid":373438,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T04:05:18.000Z","msg":"假膠味好濃"},{"pid":"2df0a0c4fd02ac005c16984a689dd0ed3414aca8","tid":2223650,"uid":201604,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T04:05:27.000Z","msg":"不了 留返條命打中共"},{"pid":"49a0ef8d1852ea85d055d098252e16f47a5a7265","tid":2223650,"u